race.description: Good Luck Without Parallel Mdn Hcp
race.comment: HOSTILE LA VISTA (6) just ran into one better when facing the starter for the first time and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Look the one they will all have to run down. SYMO'S BOY (8) has been right there in both career outings and gets the reliable Dunn/Mallyon combination. Top-three aspirations despite the sticky draw. AERIAL ARTIST (5) is at the races for the first time but has shown a bit at the trials and is drawn ideally in gate one. Respect any market confidence. STAR CHEVAL (11) returns from a break. Progressing nicely including a recent trial win at Beaudesert. In the mix.
